title: President Elbegdorj Warns of Possible Earthquake Disaster (President of Mongolia)
text: ( Source : President of Mongolia ) On October 8, President of Mongolia Tsakhiagiin Elbegdorj addressed the plenary session of the Parliament , where he reported to the Members of Parliament and the citizens about the possible earthquake
